{
  "message": "test(conformance): extend fuzz_index_align corpus with 15 edge-case seeds\n\nAdd boundary-condition and edge-case seeds for index alignment fuzz target:\n- Empty inputs: empty_left, empty_right, both_empty, seed-empty\n- Single elements: single_same, single_diff\n- Duplicates: dup_left, dup_right (test multiplicity invariants)\n- Overlap patterns: identical, no_overlap_int, mixed_overlap, interleaved\n- UTF-8: utf8_overlap, utf8_no_overlap\n- Stress: max_length (65 bytes)\n\nSeeds stored in both fuzz/corpus/ (for fuzzer) and fixtures/adversarial/\n(for deterministic tests). All 18 index_align fixture tests pass.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
